{"tid":35904,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"陳雲：關於對付政敵的道義底線問題","createTime":"2016-12-12T11:22:32.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-13T13:31:12.000Z","uid":2339,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6d8636bb564bcab040e368634086be8f5537afd9","tid":35904,"uid":2339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T11:22:32.000Z","msg":"陳雲：關於對付政敵的道義底線問題。我一向只是抨擊政敵的惡行和歪理，令對方竊據的公職位置或公益位置消失，例如喪失官位、議席或社運界的領導權。我一向不會攻擊對方與政治業務無關的生計。即使左膠及港共使出家長投訴、登報紙廣告等污穢手段令我丟失在嶺南大學的教席，我也不會反過來攻擊政敵而令他們喪失生計。尊重別人的生計與資產，是自由社會的基石，也是待人處事的厚道。<br />\n<br />\n即使他日我上台做了大總統，召開人民法庭處死賣港賊，我也會動用公帑賙濟他們的家人（如果他們沒錢供養的話）。此之謂仁政。你們不懂得華夏大道的，就繼續去胡鬧吧。君子與小人之別，是儒門大法，各位不懂得，就退回蠻荒世界去吧。<br />\n<br />\n之前，立法會要討回梁、游二人的薪酬和辦公室活動預支，我是主張只是討回辦公室活動預支，至於在正式刊憲取消議員資格之前的薪酬，我是主張按照日數（pro rata）發回。這是香港政府一向的官規，也不知為什麼到了梁振英手上，全然不顧了。"},{"pid":"b292d1820b99b72e44a5fd7eda03c54c8e342215","tid":35904,"uid":2339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T11:24:33.000Z","msg":"來源：<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=10154734278717225&amp;id=589657224\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D10154734278717225%26id%3D589657224&d=2%2FWHG351XZVBiXPaDmUC%2FgT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=fab2e4d8\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=10154734278717225&amp;id=589657224</a>"},{"pid":"c373d4e5fe1ca3759a0f4e64f9f78a9986c786f3","tid":35904,"uid":64131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T11:31:52.000Z","msg":"屌 點跟呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bc7ce154769a69a211292a1bcf4c98a89605991","tid":35904,"uid":2339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T14:04:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌 點跟呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n追隨陳雲，實踐華夏正道，是常識吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0d362bbf77426ab1b65e8ea088f631e0840652f","tid":35904,"uid":33481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T14:15:18.000Z","msg":"割蓆了"},{"pid":"d20d82f97b414bd6a7afd0b818f689ebca36c081","tid":35904,"uid":35776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T16:17:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>割蓆了</blockquote><br />\n老師好君子，好有器量<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ce8fcc30cf23bd26f66272930ece262b5833997","tid":35904,"uid":2339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T17:11:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>割蓆了</blockquote><br />\n老師好君子，好有器量<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真正追隨陳雲嘅人，邊會搞咁多屎忽嘢先至得㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"290fa62abc7595e3f761d0b2d5789bb24feba18c","tid":35904,"uid":54264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T17:19:00.000Z","msg":"又皇天擊殺又落地獄都仲講有道德底線<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27ba9ad5a793cf89d27991b701877a5d437a91e6","tid":35904,"uid":13866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T04:54:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又皇天擊殺又落地獄都仲講有道德底線<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有咩問題？"},{"pid":"691a2ab5d688bb234d6fd4ce1393f348cfdb803f","tid":35904,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T06:42:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>又皇天擊殺又落地獄都仲講有道德底線<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有咩問題？</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/03-01-2016/29086\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Farticle%2F03-01-2016%2F29086&d=2%2FWHG351XZVBiXPaDmUC%2FgT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=f0faeee0\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/03-01-2016/29086</a><br />\n<br />\n其實陳雲以前講過係唔會殺人&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n陳雲指：「香港革命建國，中國共產黨滅亡，香港賣港賊流放，永遠不得返回香港。你看，我講了這麼多的底線，從無殺人。」<br />\n<br />\n皇天擊殺的事，能算殺麼？"},{"pid":"d6861fc8c4dacd8937484c6c7ab29f812dccd2f5","tid":35904,"uid":2339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T07:31:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>又皇天擊殺又落地獄都仲講有道德底線<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有咩問題？</blockquote><br />\n耶和華喺創世記夠天火焚城、皇天擊殺地上嘅罪民啦，耶和華嘅道德底線都不知幾高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69f80c4a6ceda56a9acd836e2ebddb9c5460af3b","tid":35904,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T07:35:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>又皇天擊殺又落地獄都仲講有道德底線<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有咩問題？</blockquote><br />\n耶和華喺創世記夠天火焚城、皇天擊殺地上嘅罪民啦，耶和華嘅道德底線都不知幾高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n啦今次我就支持你<br />\n<br />\n陳雲同聖經入面既聖和華真係有幾分相似"},{"pid":"ef1a19ca75f4bd20448afca14262d4c485618366","tid":35904,"uid":2339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T13:14:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"254f77644499f0eb4614992132394dfba67be9bc","tid":35904,"uid":48157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T13:31:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}